1
00:00:01,120 --> 00:00:03,830
Hey, all you viewers out there!

2
00:00:03,830 --> 00:00:07,130
When you're watchin' Fairy Tail, make 
sure to keep the room nice and bright,

3
00:00:07,130 --> 00:00:09,220
and sit back from the screen, 'kay?

4
00:00:14,330 --> 00:00:19,660
You killed Karen, your owner?

5
00:00:21,190 --> 00:00:25,820
Spirits who kill their masters 
cannot return to the Spirit World.

6
00:00:25,820 --> 00:00:28,720
I will now start to disappear.

7
00:00:28,720 --> 00:00:30,910
In front of her grave...

8
00:00:31,870 --> 00:00:33,290
But, that's...

9
00:00:54,220 --> 00:00:58,630
It'll be all right! I'll yell it out countless times.

10
00:00:58,630 --> 00:01:03,700
I believe your every tomorrow will be shining.

11
00:01:03,700 --> 00:01:06,050
The intersection of all people

12
00:01:06,050 --> 00:01:08,660
whose dreams have come true is one point:

13
00:01:08,660 --> 00:01:13,290
Never giving up.  And that's why we're not gonna lose!

14
00:01:13,290 --> 00:01:18,470
When it seems like you'll be blown away by the headwinds,

15
00:01:18,470 --> 00:01:20,620
grasp this hand, try to take a chance.

16
00:01:20,620 --> 00:01:23,890
Because you're not alone anymore, got it?

17
00:01:27,010 --> 00:01:29,000
Go forward, more and more!

18
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:31,520
Don't give up on your awesome dream!

19
00:01:31,520 --> 00:01:32,780
That's right, don't cry!

20
00:01:32,780 --> 00:01:34,250
Move on, my way!

21
00:01:34,250 --> 00:01:36,630
Now, with the light shining down upon you.

22
00:01:36,630 --> 00:01:38,710
Don't even think about something like giving up!

23
00:01:38,710 --> 00:01:41,140
Even if you trade being hurt again for strength.

24
00:01:41,140 --> 00:01:46,630
Your eyes, always looking straight ahead,

25
00:01:46,630 --> 00:01:50,910
can surely see the light!

26
00:02:08,530 --> 00:02:10,630
It all started three years ago...

27
00:02:11,230 --> 00:02:15,410
Sorry, I'm heading to the spa now.

28
00:02:15,410 --> 00:02:17,240
You be good boys and run home now.

29
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:20,760
Hey, what about our date today?

30
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:18,690
What's with her?

31
00:02:18,690 --> 00:02:20,760
She's got another harem?

32
00:02:20,760 --> 00:02:21,530
Ugh.

33
00:02:23,210 --> 00:02:25,790
Oh, Karen my dear, you're back?

34
00:02:25,790 --> 00:02:28,660
If I must...

35
00:02:28,660 --> 00:02:31,570
Gate of the Ram, I open thee!

36
00:02:31,880 --> 00:02:33,560
Aries!

37
00:02:35,590 --> 00:02:38,730
Um... Did you call me?

38
00:02:38,730 --> 00:02:40,220
I'm sorry...

39
00:02:40,220 --> 00:02:40,970
Oh-boy!

40
00:02:40,650 --> 00:02:42,120
She's fluffy and cute!

41
00:02:40,970 --> 00:02:42,120
There she is!

42
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:43,080
Aries!

43
00:02:43,080 --> 00:02:46,520
Do me a favor and keep them company, 'kay?

44
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:48,550
B-But, I...

45
00:02:48,550 --> 00:02:49,900
I'm sorry!

46
00:02:49,900 --> 00:02:51,480
Fine by me.

47
00:02:49,920 --> 00:02:51,480
Let's play, fluffy-wuffy...

48
00:02:51,730 --> 00:02:56,480
I'm not a spirit for entertaining men, though...

49
00:02:56,480 --> 00:02:59,950
Are you disobeying my orders, huh?

50
00:02:59,950 --> 00:03:01,320
I'm sorry!

51
00:03:01,320 --> 00:03:02,430
Okay, then it's settled!

52
00:03:02,430 --> 00:03:04,780
Let's play, Aries!

53
00:03:03,450 --> 00:03:04,780
Let's go for a drive in my magic wheels!

54
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:09,090
The Spirit King!

55
00:03:12,350 --> 00:03:16,480
Honestly, when a spirit starts 
talking back to her master...

56
00:03:16,480 --> 00:03:18,280
What's the world coming to?

57
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:22,970
Karen, deary... Don't go 
treating your spirits so badly.

58
00:03:24,320 --> 00:03:28,140
I'm free to use my property 
as I see fit, aren't I?

59
00:03:29,340 --> 00:03:31,920
Little Aries seems like she's suffering.

60
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:40,020
Like when you used her as a shield to 
block the opposing wizard's attack...

61
00:03:41,810 --> 00:03:44,430
I'm sorry!

62
00:03:45,100 --> 00:03:49,000
Suffering? Spirits don't 
have feelings like that.

63
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:51,510
They're just tools.

64
00:03:51,920 --> 00:03:52,920
Karen!

65
00:03:53,540 --> 00:03:55,870
Spirits are living things, too!

66
00:03:55,870 --> 00:04:00,140
Treat them poorly, and <i>you'll </i>
be the one suffering next!

67
00:04:04,430 --> 00:04:07,740
Don't bring your petty grievances to the master!

68
00:04:07,740 --> 00:04:11,160
No! I didn't say a thing!

69
00:04:11,160 --> 00:04:11,980
I'm sorry...

70
00:04:12,220 --> 00:04:16,730
Making Master Bob angry at 
me is no laughing matter!

71
00:04:18,300 --> 00:04:20,980
I-I didn't... I'm sorry...

72
00:04:20,980 --> 00:04:23,390
Playing innocent, are you?

73
00:04:23,390 --> 00:04:24,820
What are you going to do?

74
00:04:24,820 --> 00:04:29,700
As punishment, I will have you stay 
in the human world for seven days.

75
00:04:30,030 --> 00:04:33,450
Seven days? But you don't have that 
sort of magical power, Madame Karen.

76
00:04:33,450 --> 00:04:34,590
I'm sorry!

77
00:04:34,590 --> 00:04:37,520
I wouldn't underestimate me if I were you.

78
00:04:37,960 --> 00:04:41,120
You'd do better to worry about yourself.

79
00:04:41,120 --> 00:04:45,620
I wonder what'll happen to a Spirit that 
stays in the human world for seven days?

80
00:04:46,350 --> 00:04:48,130
I'm curious...

81
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:50,930
P-Please stop...

82
00:04:50,930 --> 00:04:52,350
I'm sorry.

83
00:04:54,140 --> 00:04:55,390
Running away?

84
00:04:55,390 --> 00:04:57,980
It's no use! I'll call you back 
as many times as it takes!

85
00:04:59,150 --> 00:05:02,340
You're wrong. I forcibly 
switched places with her.

86
00:05:02,340 --> 00:05:03,400
It's you...

87
00:05:03,710 --> 00:05:06,350
Let it go, Karen.

88
00:05:06,350 --> 00:05:08,380
Leo, the Lion.

89
00:05:09,540 --> 00:05:11,740
That's how I was back then.

90
00:05:11,740 --> 00:05:16,090
Aries and I were both bound 
by contract to Karen.

91
00:05:17,940 --> 00:05:20,780
How dare you open the gate on your own!

92
00:05:20,780 --> 00:05:24,610
I'm a spirit designed for 
battle and quite tough.

93
00:05:24,610 --> 00:05:28,090
I can overlook a bit of mistreatment.

94
00:05:28,390 --> 00:05:34,980
But if you continue to do such horrible 
things to Aries, I will not forgive you.

95
00:05:35,660 --> 00:05:38,870
And what do you, a spirit, plan to do about it?

96
00:05:38,870 --> 00:05:41,820
I think I should just tell 
you straight out today...

97
00:05:41,820 --> 00:05:44,820
I want you to release Aries 
and me from our contracts.

98
00:05:45,490 --> 00:05:46,820
What?

99
00:05:47,150 --> 00:05:50,250
I cannot bear watching your evil actions.

100
00:05:50,250 --> 00:05:54,310
The other spirits fear their keys 
coming into your possession.

101
00:05:54,310 --> 00:05:55,910
Shut up! Silence!

102
00:05:55,910 --> 00:05:58,210
You are a disgrace to Celestial Wizards.

103
00:05:58,210 --> 00:05:59,560
Go back!

104
00:05:59,560 --> 00:06:02,660
Gate of the Lion, close!

105
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:10,680
Close!

106
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:11,680
Close!

107
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:14,270
Go back, Leo!

108
00:06:18,080 --> 00:06:20,770
Why can't I do a forced closure?

109
00:06:20,770 --> 00:06:26,050
Until you release us from your contract, 
I have no intention of going back.

110
00:06:26,470 --> 00:06:30,610
While I am here, you can't 
call any other spirits.

111
00:06:30,870 --> 00:06:36,370
With your magical power, you aren't able to 
call more than one spirit at the same time after all.

112
00:06:36,620 --> 00:06:39,870
That'll be quite a problem for you, yes?

113
00:06:39,870 --> 00:06:42,860
I wonder if this will go as you plan?

114
00:06:43,550 --> 00:06:45,840
Your magical power isn't infinite, either.

115
00:06:46,090 --> 00:06:53,050
In ten days, my magical power will be used up, 
and you'll be forced to go back to the Spirit World.

116
00:06:53,300 --> 00:06:57,370
No. I used my own magical power to come here.

117
00:06:57,370 --> 00:06:59,810
Your magical power is irrelevant.

118
00:07:00,060 --> 00:07:02,340
I'll stay here no matter how many days it takes.

119
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:05,190
There are some ruins to the west of town.

120
00:07:05,810 --> 00:07:08,140
If you reconsider, come see me.

121
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:16,910
How dare he!

122
00:07:22,910 --> 00:07:24,980
Come back, Leo!

123
00:07:24,980 --> 00:07:27,630
Aren't you basically at your limit?

124
00:07:27,630 --> 00:07:31,170
The Lion is the leader of the 12 Zodiac Gates.

125
00:07:31,170 --> 00:07:35,010
Things that the other spirits 
can't handle, I can.

126
00:07:35,010 --> 00:07:39,680
Until you release us from our contracts, 
I won't leave the human world.

127
00:07:40,310 --> 00:07:41,690
You've got to be kidding me!

128
00:07:41,690 --> 00:07:45,180
You expect me to give up two 
of the 12 Zodiac gate keys?

129
00:07:45,180 --> 00:07:49,370
With you, I can earn a whole lot more money!

130
00:07:49,860 --> 00:07:51,150
Go away.

131
00:07:51,750 --> 00:07:54,610
When you feel like releasing us, come back.

132
00:07:54,610 --> 00:07:56,120
Why, you...

133
00:08:01,700 --> 00:08:02,790
Come on...

134
00:08:02,790 --> 00:08:05,170
It's been a month already.

135
00:08:05,170 --> 00:08:09,750
I can't do any work with you doing this!

136
00:08:09,750 --> 00:08:13,940
I promise... I won't mistreat Aries any more.

137
00:08:14,250 --> 00:08:15,510
Promise?

138
00:08:15,770 --> 00:08:17,380
You're a liar.

139
00:08:17,650 --> 00:08:21,720
If you really regret what 
you did, you'd let us free.

140
00:08:23,320 --> 00:08:24,380
Damn you!

141
00:08:24,380 --> 00:08:26,290
Go to hell and die!

142
00:08:26,290 --> 00:08:29,050
If you disappear, I can call Aries again!

143
00:08:29,050 --> 00:08:31,540
It's all 'cause you're here!

144
00:08:32,800 --> 00:08:36,010
This is all your fault, damn you!

145
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:43,820
I'm getting used to being in the Human World.

146
00:08:46,710 --> 00:08:52,760
I can't really stop my life-force from 
eroding, but I'm not suffering like before.

147
00:08:54,550 --> 00:08:56,330
It's been three months...

148
00:08:56,330 --> 00:08:59,100
Maybe I should forgive Karen now.

149
00:08:59,350 --> 00:09:03,780
If she mistreats Aries again, 
I can always save her once more.

150
00:09:14,520 --> 00:09:16,100
It can't be!

151
00:09:16,760 --> 00:09:21,780
She took on a job recklessly 
without my permission.

152
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:26,540
She must have been horribly impatient 
not being able to work for three months.

153
00:09:27,660 --> 00:09:31,210
But Karen shouldn't have been 
able to call any spirits!

154
00:09:31,800 --> 00:09:32,700
And yet...

155
00:09:33,050 --> 00:09:37,000
A wizard using a large amount
of magical power at once

156
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:41,760
should be able to call forth
two spirits at the same time.

157
00:09:41,760 --> 00:09:44,140
Karen was betting on that.

158
00:09:44,390 --> 00:09:49,190
But in the end her body wasn't able to take it.

159
00:09:50,230 --> 00:09:55,290
All I wanted was for Karen 
to rethink her actions...

160
00:09:55,770 --> 00:09:58,100
To realize that spirits aren't tools...

161
00:09:59,100 --> 00:10:04,080
That we have free will, that 
we have hearts of our own...

162
00:10:04,080 --> 00:10:06,120
That's all I wanted...

163
00:10:06,790 --> 00:10:08,200
This...

164
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:11,250
This isn't what I wanted!

165
00:10:11,820 --> 00:10:13,210
Karen!

166
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:18,680
Karen!

167
00:10:22,520 --> 00:10:25,930
That is the sin I committed.

168
00:10:26,370 --> 00:10:30,300
Human life cannot be returned once it is lost.

169
00:10:30,300 --> 00:10:33,650
The dead never return, for eternity.

170
00:10:33,910 --> 00:10:38,170
The only way to repent is 
for me to disappear myself.

171
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:42,370
Loke, hey!

172
00:10:43,760 --> 00:10:45,850
I guess it's about time...

173
00:10:45,850 --> 00:10:47,080
Time? Time for what?

174
00:10:47,920 --> 00:10:50,710
Time for me to disappear...

175
00:10:50,710 --> 00:10:52,470
What are you talking about?

176
00:10:54,140 --> 00:10:55,390
Karen...

177
00:11:02,470 --> 00:11:06,200
Ever since that day, I've been unable 
to return to the Spirit World.

178
00:11:06,200 --> 00:11:07,600
Y-Your hand...

179
00:11:07,850 --> 00:11:11,810
It's the law of the Spirit World. The rules.

180
00:11:11,810 --> 00:11:14,110
I can't do anything about it.

181
00:11:14,630 --> 00:11:19,490
I was never able to forget 
about Karen since then.

182
00:11:19,840 --> 00:11:25,140
I tried a lot of things to get my mind 
off it, but I could never forget.

183
00:11:26,450 --> 00:11:30,910
I've simply been persisting 
until this time came.

184
00:11:30,910 --> 00:11:34,460
Until the moment I disappear 
in front of Karen's grave.

185
00:11:34,690 --> 00:11:38,590
And, at long last, the time has come.

186
00:11:39,030 --> 00:11:45,380
Thank you, Lucy, for letting me meet a truly 
wonderful Celestial Wizard in the end...

187
00:11:45,380 --> 00:11:48,180
Wait! I'll save you! Don't give up!

188
00:11:48,510 --> 00:11:51,920
Give my regards to everyone at Fairy Tail...

189
00:11:54,490 --> 00:11:55,320
No!

190
00:11:55,320 --> 00:11:56,730
Lucy...

191
00:11:56,730 --> 00:11:58,610
I won't accept this!

192
00:11:59,140 --> 00:12:04,270
If you return to the Spirit World, your 
life-force will recover really quickly!

193
00:12:04,270 --> 00:12:06,820
I'll make it so you can return!

194
00:12:08,230 --> 00:12:10,480
You can't do that...

195
00:12:10,480 --> 00:12:13,010
The law is the law...

196
00:12:13,550 --> 00:12:16,820
But... This is wrong!

197
00:12:16,820 --> 00:12:19,900
You didn't actually kill Karen!

198
00:12:19,900 --> 00:12:21,800
It was just an unfortunate accident!

199
00:12:22,170 --> 00:12:22,970
Lucy...

200
00:12:23,220 --> 00:12:25,270
Gate of the Lion, I open thee!

201
00:12:25,270 --> 00:12:27,850
Return Loke to the Spirit World!

202
00:12:28,420 --> 00:12:30,750
Open! Please!

203
00:12:31,470 --> 00:12:33,150
Open!

204
00:12:33,150 --> 00:12:36,350
Lucy... That's enough. Please stop...

205
00:12:36,930 --> 00:12:38,340
I won't stop!

206
00:12:38,340 --> 00:12:42,360
I can't stand by when a friend of 
mine is disappearing before my eyes!

207
00:12:46,950 --> 00:12:51,080
Gate of the Lion, I open thee!

208
00:12:51,080 --> 00:12:55,060
Lucy! Don't use so much 
magical power all at once!

209
00:12:55,060 --> 00:12:58,460
I said I'm going to save you, no matter what!

210
00:12:58,710 --> 00:13:04,970
I can force open the gate to 
the Spirit World... Watch me!

211
00:13:05,170 --> 00:13:06,230
Stop it!

212
00:13:06,230 --> 00:13:08,690
Gate of the Lion, I open thee!

213
00:13:08,690 --> 00:13:10,390
Open!

214
00:13:10,390 --> 00:13:12,120
It won't open!

215
00:13:12,120 --> 00:13:16,890
Spirits who let their contracted owner 
die can't go back to the Spirit World!

216
00:13:19,610 --> 00:13:20,950
Please, stop!

217
00:13:20,950 --> 00:13:23,330
You're starting to erode along with me!

218
00:13:23,330 --> 00:13:26,010
At this rate you'll disappear when I do!

219
00:13:26,010 --> 00:13:27,490
You won't die!

220
00:13:27,490 --> 00:13:29,420
I won't let you die...

221
00:13:29,420 --> 00:13:34,880
What's the point of magic to begin with 
if I can't use it protect my friends?

222
00:13:35,820 --> 00:13:37,580
Stop it!

223
00:13:37,580 --> 00:13:41,590
Don't make my crime any 
worse than it already is!

224
00:13:41,590 --> 00:13:42,930
What crime?!

225
00:13:42,930 --> 00:13:48,730
If that's the rule of the Spirit 
World, then I'll change it!

226
00:14:08,980 --> 00:14:10,340
What's that?

227
00:14:10,340 --> 00:14:11,370
It can't be...

228
00:14:11,370 --> 00:14:12,780
That's the...

229
00:14:13,240 --> 00:14:14,790
...Spirit King?

230
00:14:17,780 --> 00:14:19,810
Why are you here?

231
00:14:20,070 --> 00:14:23,990
The King? You mean the ruler of the Spirits?

232
00:14:24,250 --> 00:14:26,800
Old friend.

233
00:14:27,880 --> 00:14:36,440
It is forbidden for we who have compacted with 
humans to kill the one who possesses the key.

234
00:14:39,490 --> 00:14:44,310
It matters not if it was direct or indirect.

235
00:14:44,310 --> 00:14:50,280
Leo the Lion, you are no longer allowed 
to return to the Spirit World.

236
00:14:50,280 --> 00:14:53,110
Hey, that's going too far!

237
00:14:53,110 --> 00:14:55,170
Don't, Lucy!

238
00:14:55,170 --> 00:14:59,460
Old friend... Human girl...

239
00:14:59,460 --> 00:15:03,080
That law shall not be changed.

240
00:15:03,690 --> 00:15:09,010
Wait, did he show himself because Lucy 
blurted out that she'd change the rule?

241
00:15:09,010 --> 00:15:12,420
Just for that, the King came himself?

242
00:15:12,420 --> 00:15:15,930
For three years... Loke's been 
suffering for three years!

243
00:15:16,280 --> 00:15:19,590
For his friend! For Aries!

244
00:15:19,590 --> 00:15:21,390
What else could he do?

245
00:15:22,060 --> 00:15:28,730
I too am pained by my old friend's wish...

246
00:15:28,730 --> 00:15:30,370
What are you talking about?

247
00:15:30,370 --> 00:15:32,490
He's not your "old" friend!

248
00:15:32,490 --> 00:15:35,950
He's your friend, right now, before your eyes!

249
00:15:36,200 --> 00:15:38,450
Listen to me, Mustache Man!

250
00:15:39,080 --> 00:15:41,410
Mustache?

251
00:15:41,410 --> 00:15:42,850
L-Lucy...

252
00:15:42,850 --> 00:15:44,750
This was an unfortunate accident.

253
00:15:44,750 --> 00:15:47,210
Loke didn't do anything wrong!

254
00:15:47,460 --> 00:15:49,580
I won't accept anything but 
his complete innocence!

255
00:15:49,580 --> 00:15:52,170
I won't accept it!

256
00:15:53,910 --> 00:15:55,840
Enough, Lucy...

257
00:15:55,840 --> 00:15:58,810
I don't want anybody to forgive me...

258
00:15:59,080 --> 00:16:01,530
I want to repent for my sins!

259
00:16:01,820 --> 00:16:05,510
I just want to disappear!

260
00:16:07,440 --> 00:16:10,400
You can't!

261
00:16:11,900 --> 00:16:15,610
You disappearing isn't 
going to bring Karen back!

262
00:16:15,610 --> 00:16:18,370
All it will do is create more sadness!

263
00:16:20,740 --> 00:16:22,650
It's not a crime!

264
00:16:22,650 --> 00:16:26,560
Caring about your friends is not a crime!

265
00:16:26,560 --> 00:16:29,940
This many spirits... All at once...

266
00:16:29,940 --> 00:16:32,090
Even Karen couldn't do this...

267
00:16:32,870 --> 00:16:41,140
If you disappear, then Aries, myself, and 
everyone else here will be filled with sadness!

268
00:16:41,380 --> 00:16:46,210
You won't be repenting for 
your sins at all that way!

269
00:16:54,850 --> 00:16:56,360
Lucy!

270
00:16:59,890 --> 00:17:05,380
All my friends came forward to 
show that they feel the same way.

271
00:17:05,380 --> 00:17:06,330
Your friends?

272
00:17:06,980 --> 00:17:12,010
If you're a spirit too, then you 
should know how Loke and Aries felt!

273
00:17:12,740 --> 00:17:16,020
Lucy, why are you forcing yourself like this?

274
00:17:16,020 --> 00:17:17,890
You want to follow in Karen's footsteps?

275
00:17:21,980 --> 00:17:26,030
If my old friend goes so far as to say that...

276
00:17:26,300 --> 00:17:31,360
Perhaps it is the law that is in error.

277
00:17:32,200 --> 00:17:36,310
Leo, who committed the crime 
for his brethren Aries.

278
00:17:36,310 --> 00:17:40,110
And you, old friend, who 
tried to save that Leo...

279
00:17:41,630 --> 00:17:47,160
Considering the beauty of that bond, I 
will make an exception for this incident.

280
00:17:47,160 --> 00:17:54,280
Leo, I give thee warrant to 
return to the Spirit World.

281
00:17:56,110 --> 00:17:59,080
You ain't so bad, Mustache Man!

282
00:18:02,190 --> 00:18:04,010
You are pardoned.

283
00:18:04,010 --> 00:18:07,330
Be grateful to the star's guidance.

284
00:18:08,550 --> 00:18:09,940
Wait, please...

285
00:18:10,510 --> 00:18:11,860
I...

286
00:18:12,440 --> 00:18:23,080
If you still wish to repent for your sins, 
I order you to aid your friend and live on.

287
00:18:25,950 --> 00:18:29,930
I believe her to be a friend of such worth.

288
00:18:29,930 --> 00:18:33,420
You should protect her with your life.

289
00:18:42,720 --> 00:18:44,170
You heard the man.

290
00:18:57,870 --> 00:18:59,220
Lucy...

291
00:19:00,040 --> 00:19:00,850
Yeah.

292
00:19:02,110 --> 00:19:05,150
Thank you, Lucy...

293
00:19:13,410 --> 00:19:14,880
A spirit?

294
00:19:14,880 --> 00:19:16,270
You're a spirit, Loke?

295
00:19:16,270 --> 00:19:18,450
Yup, that's the deal.

296
00:19:18,890 --> 00:19:23,350
So that weird feeling when we switched 
places that time was from that!

297
00:19:23,350 --> 00:19:24,770
Yup, that's what it was.

298
00:19:24,770 --> 00:19:27,490
I didn't notice at all!

299
00:19:27,490 --> 00:19:30,810
But wait... You're not a 
cow or a horse or nothin'.

300
00:19:30,810 --> 00:19:34,150
You know Virgo, Natsu. She 
has a human form, remember?

301
00:19:34,150 --> 00:19:36,780
Yeah, but she can turn into a gorilla.

302
00:19:36,780 --> 00:19:38,190
Oh, yeah. That's true.

303
00:19:38,550 --> 00:19:40,590
Loke's the Lion Spirit.

304
00:19:40,590 --> 00:19:41,430
Lion?!

305
00:19:41,430 --> 00:19:43,320
A grown-up cat!

306
00:19:43,320 --> 00:19:44,000
That's right.

307
00:19:44,000 --> 00:19:45,600
No, it's not!

308
00:19:46,310 --> 00:19:47,540
Cool...

309
00:19:48,040 --> 00:19:51,400
But are you feeling okay?

310
00:19:51,400 --> 00:19:54,920
I'm not 100% yet, but I figured 
I'd come to say hi to everyone.

311
00:19:55,170 --> 00:19:58,600
And I wanted to see Lucy 
again as soon as possible.

312
00:19:59,530 --> 00:20:01,230
He lllllikes you!

313
00:20:01,230 --> 00:20:02,800
Stop rolling your tongue!

314
00:20:02,800 --> 00:20:06,620
So let's talk, you and I, about the future!

315
00:20:06,620 --> 00:20:07,820
Hey, now!

316
00:20:07,820 --> 00:20:08,680
Man, I'm jealous.

317
00:20:08,680 --> 00:20:10,580
I wish I had a spirit.

318
00:20:10,580 --> 00:20:11,730
What kind of spirit?

319
00:20:11,730 --> 00:20:13,700
A dragon, duh!

320
00:20:13,700 --> 00:20:15,870
Then I could test out my 
Dragon Slayer magic for real!

321
00:20:16,930 --> 00:20:20,250
Spirits aren't things you 
summon to test your strength!

322
00:20:20,250 --> 00:20:21,150
That's right.

323
00:20:21,400 --> 00:20:23,850
Spirits are for spinning tales of love...

324
00:20:22,730 --> 00:20:24,600
You, go back already...

325
00:20:24,600 --> 00:20:27,160
You're still not fully recovered, right?

326
00:20:27,160 --> 00:20:28,680
Wait a second.

327
00:20:29,150 --> 00:20:30,540
Here!

328
00:20:30,540 --> 00:20:31,660
What are these?

329
00:20:31,660 --> 00:20:33,830
Tickets for a resort hotel.

330
00:20:34,080 --> 00:20:36,500
You guys really helped me out a lot.

331
00:20:36,500 --> 00:20:38,010
Fish!

332
00:20:36,500 --> 00:20:39,260
I've never stayed at a hotel as fancy as that!

333
00:20:39,380 --> 00:20:43,250
I already gave Erza hers, so please have fun.

334
00:20:43,250 --> 00:20:44,330
Hey, people!

335
00:20:44,330 --> 00:20:45,680
What are you standing around for?

336
00:20:46,000 --> 00:20:47,600
Want me to leave you behind?

337
00:20:47,600 --> 00:20:49,010
Now that's fast!

338
00:20:49,010 --> 00:20:50,580
Yeah, let's go!

339
00:20:50,580 --> 00:20:52,650
I'll head off just like this!

340
00:20:52,650 --> 00:20:53,830
Me, too!

341
00:20:53,830 --> 00:20:56,560
Idiot, I have to pack for a 
trip a little, so hold up.

342
00:20:54,660 --> 00:20:55,780
Lucy...

343
00:20:56,870 --> 00:20:59,900
It's not like my sins have
completely disappeared,

344
00:20:59,900 --> 00:21:03,510
but you've given me the
confidence now to move on.

345
00:21:03,510 --> 00:21:09,200
Where once I was a member of Fairy 
Tail, now I am your spirit, Lucy.

346
00:21:09,780 --> 00:21:12,920
I'll show up whenever my owner's in trouble.

347
00:21:12,920 --> 00:21:15,870
Think of me as your prince on a white horse.

348
00:21:16,120 --> 00:21:17,790
I'm not your owner.

349
00:21:18,440 --> 00:21:19,890
I'm your friend, right?

350
00:21:20,970 --> 00:21:22,380
That's right.

351
00:21:22,700 --> 00:21:25,400
From now on, let's count on each other, Lucy.

352
00:21:25,720 --> 00:21:29,490
Same to you, Loke!

353
00:21:31,000 --> 00:21:33,250
Lucy, we're leaving.

354
00:21:33,500 --> 00:21:35,320
So, Erza...

355
00:21:35,320 --> 00:21:36,430
If...

356
00:21:37,400 --> 00:21:48,110
If someone here was hurt or lost their life 
because of me, I think I'd suffer a lot like Loke.

357
00:21:48,380 --> 00:21:50,620
But, it's okay.

358
00:21:50,620 --> 00:21:55,740
Because if we all work together, we can 
overcome any trouble we might have, right?

359
00:21:55,740 --> 00:21:57,710
You couldn't have said it better.

360
00:21:57,710 --> 00:21:58,590
Yeah!

361
00:21:59,080 --> 00:22:01,450
Hey, let's hurry and go!

362
00:22:01,450 --> 00:22:02,550
Aye, sir!

363
00:22:02,550 --> 00:22:05,220
Let's party all day and night, non-stop!

364
00:22:05,220 --> 00:22:09,380
It's a favor from Loke, so we're 
going to have lots of fun!

365
00:22:09,580 --> 00:22:11,430
Aye, sir!

366
00:22:12,950 --> 00:22:19,000
There was no way I could have
known that before long,

367
00:22:20,880 --> 00:22:24,520
Erza's smile would disappear...

368
00:23:56,130 --> 00:23:57,590
Hey, hey, Natsu!

369
00:23:57,590 --> 00:23:59,110
I'm going to head out for a bit!

370
00:23:59,110 --> 00:23:59,990
Upa!

371
00:23:59,990 --> 00:24:02,200
Wow, you're really rarin' to go.

372
00:24:02,200 --> 00:24:03,090
Where are you going?

373
00:24:03,090 --> 00:24:05,420
Aye! I'm going to Heaven on earth!

374
00:24:05,420 --> 00:24:06,480
What are you talking about?

375
00:24:06,480 --> 00:24:07,850
Did you hit your head or something?

376
00:24:07,850 --> 00:24:09,750
You'll know if you come with me.

377
00:24:10,420 --> 00:24:13,170
What's with you? You're creepin' me out...

378
00:24:13,470 --> 00:24:16,090
Next time: Tower of Heaven!

379
00:24:16,330 --> 00:24:19,250
Huh? A fish restaurant?

380
00:24:19,250 --> 00:24:22,250
This is my paradise!

381
00:24:21,600 --> 00:24:24,350
Happy, don't leave me!

382
00:24:24,350 --> 00:24:26,420


